sequenceDiagram
    autonumber
    participant Payer as Payer (Fan / Stripe-on-Sui)
    participant PTB as PTB execute_split
    participant Config as SplitConfig (shared)
    participant Proto as ProtocolConfig (shared, read-only)
    participant Tax as TaxVault (shared)
    participant Sav as SavingsVault (shared)
    participant Scallop as Scallop USDC pool
    participant R as Recipients (N wallets)
    participant Trez as Treasury (protocol)
    participant Idx as Indexer (gRPC)

    Payer->>PTB: Coin<USDC>, include_yield, expected_version
    PTB->>Config: read recipients, bps, version
    PTB->>Proto: read treasury, fee bounds
    PTB-->>PTB: assert version match & fee in bounds
    PTB->>R: transfer N slices
    PTB->>Trez: transfer protocol_fee slice
    PTB->>Tax: deposit(tax_coin)
    alt include_yield && strategy set
        PTB->>Scallop: deposit(yield_slice)
        Note over PTB,Scallop: abort here reverts the WHOLE PTB<br/>(no in-Move fallback); client retries include_yield=false
        Scallop-->>Sav: yield position ref stored
    else yield off / Scallop-skip retry
        PTB->>Sav: deposit(savings_coin incl. yield_slice)
    end
    PTB->>Sav: deposit(remaining savings_coin)
    PTB-->>Idx: emit SplitExecuted
    Idx-->>R: notify (off-chain, v1)
